songs.title: Just Soprano Freestyle

I'm Michael Jordan, Scottie Pippen and Pac's son
I'm Phil Jackson, this is South Side

But I still might throw on a little (?) on

Place I got my hoes from
Talkin', tell me if you know somethin'
